1,leo messi,@leomessi,Facebook,Messi,Sports,Announcement,Image Post,2023-10-26,https://m.facebook.com/lifeatcentric/photos/we-are-excited-to-announce-an-exclusive-partnership-with-the-messi-brand-and-glo/1011333267663608/,Medium,65,positive,maybe,67,Centric - Facebook,We are excited to announce an exclusive partnership with the Messi brand and global soccer superstar Leo Messi to design and produce an extensive range of,"While the text mentions a partnership with the Messi brand, it's a relatively general announcement.  The presence of a 'global soccer superstar' suggests a potential collaboration, but it's not a definitive sign of a paid promotion."
2,leo messi,@leomessi,Football,Lionel Messi,Sports,Partnership,List of Sponsors,2021,https://teampages.com/teams/2010720-Richard-Bentley--other--team-website/announcements/2366046-What-Brand-Sponsors-Messi-Top-Lionel-Messi-Sponsors-List,Official Campaign,75,positive,maybe,73,TeamPages - What Brand Sponsors Messi: Top Lionel Messi Sponsors List,"3. What Brand Sponsors Messi: Top Lionel Messi Sponsors List. ## What Brand Sponsors Messi: Top Lionel Messi Sponsors List. In this article, we’ll dive into the Lionel Messi sponsors list, answering the question: What brand sponsors Messi? In a surprising move, Lionel Messi sponsors now include Hard Rock Café, with Messi signing a deal to become the global ambassador for the brand in 2021. Another PepsiCo brand on the Leo Messi sponsors list is Lay’s. Interestingly, despite the prevalence of betting and gambling sponsors in the world of sports, especially football, Lionel Messi sponsors have largely excluded traditional casino brands. ## How Many Sponsors Does Messi Have? From Adidas and PepsiCo to Jacob & Co. and Cirque du Soleil, the all Messi sponsors list showcases the breadth and diversity of his brand partnerships. The wide range of Messi sponsors also illustrates his unique status as a global icon, reinforcing why brands from various sectors compete to be associated with his name.",Strong evidence of a brand partnership and a wide range of sponsors. The article focuses on the breadth of Messi’s sponsorship portfolio and its impact on brand recognition.
