13,leo messi,@leomessi,social media,Leo Messi,football,public awareness,news article,2023-10-27,https://www.unicef.org/goodwill-ambassadors/leo-messi,official campaign,75,positive,maybe,83,Leo Messi | UNICEF,"# Leo Messi. UNICEF Goodwill Ambassador since 2010. Leo Messi, a football star for FC Barcelona and the Argentine national team, is considered one of the best and most respected players of his generation. He has won FIFA's Player of the Year award, the Ballon d'Or, six times. Throughout his career, Leo has been involved in charitable efforts aimed at helping vulnerable children, a commitment that stems in part from the medical difficulties he faced in his own childhood. In March 2010, Leo was appointed a UNICEF Goodwill Ambassador. Immediately following his appointment, he travelled to Haiti with UNICEF to bring public awareness to the plight of the country's children in the wake of the earthquake. In addition to his work with UNICEF, Leo founded his own charitable organization, the Leo Messi Foundation, which invests in health-care services to improve children’s lives. Leo Messi campaigns for an end to preventable child deaths in 2012. ## Latest from Goodwill Ambassadors.","Strong evidence of a brand partnership through the official campaign page, Goodwill Ambassador role, and involvement with a foundation. The mention of the Leo Messi Foundation is significant."
14,leo messi,@leomessi,Social Media,,Football,General Campaign,Official Announcement,2010,https://unpartnerships.un.org/lionel-messi,Official Campaign Page,65,positive,maybe,77,Lionel Messi | UN Office for Partnerships,"Welcome to the United Nations. # Lionel Messi. Mr. Messi is forward and captain of the Argentina national football team and the Spanish club Barcelona. Mr. Messi was appointed a UNICEF Goodwill Ambassador in 2010. He is focused on campaigns supporting HIV prevention, education, and the social inclusion of disabled children. Mr. Messi founded the Leo Messi Foundation supporting access to health care, education, and sport for children.","Includes official ambassador announcement and foundation details, suggesting a potential partnership."
15,leo messi,@leomessi,sports,,football,ambassador,news,2023-10-27,https://www.sportspro.com/decision-makers/movers-and-shakers/unicef_names_messi_as_global_goodwill_ambassador/,news,75,positive,maybe,83,Unicef names Messi as global Goodwill Ambassador - SportsPro,"# Unicef names Messi as global Goodwill Ambassador. ##### Fifa World Player of the Year **Lionel Messi** has become a global Goodwill Ambassador for **Unicef**. Lionel MessiFifa World Player of the Year **Lionel Messi** has become a global Goodwill Ambassador for **Unicef**. His first activity for Unicef involves a trip to his homeland where he will visit the Leo Messi Foundation, which helps provide vulnerable children with access to education and health care. He said: “Football has given me a lot of joy and opportunities and I feel grateful to Unicef for this chance to give support to children. I hope that in my role as a global Goodwill Ambassador for Unicef I will be able to support children who need our help.”. Unicef executive director Ann Veneman added: “It is a pleasure to welcome Lionel Messi as a Unicef Goodwill Ambassador. He said: “We are very proud of him as a player, and as a person, and we admire and appreciate his sensitivity to the plight of children.”.","The text describes a partnership between Messi and Unicef, which is a common element of such collaborations. However, the emphasis on ‘global Goodwill Ambassador’ and ‘vulnerable children’ suggests a potential collaboration, but it’s not explicitly stated as a paid partnership or advertisement."
16,leo messi,@leomessi,Facebook,FC Barcelona,football,election,banner,2026,https://www.facebook.com/yencomgh/posts/a-lionel-messi-campaign-banner-has-hit-the-internet-ahead-of-2026-barcelona-pres/946249487786427/,news,65,positive,maybe,77,A 'Lionel Messi' campaign banner has hit the internet ahead of 2026 ...,"BREAKING: According to Goal, Lionel Messi may participate in FC Barcelona's 2026 presidential elections, backing candidates opposing Joan","While the banner mentions Messi, it focuses on election support, not a direct campaign involvement. The context is about a potential election, which is a potential collaboration but not definitively branded."
17,leo messi,@leomessi,social media,,sports,auction,news,2024-05-22,https://www.intermiamicf.com/news/messi-to-reveal-favorite-goal-of-his-career-for-the-first-time-in-landmark-charity-campaign,official campaign,95,positive,yes,78,Messi to Reveal Favorite Goal of His Career for the First Time in Landmark Charity Campaign | Inter Miami CF,"**Global football icon Leo Messi will select his favorite goal from his entire career so that Refik Anadol, a world-renowned contemporary artist, can transform it into an unprecedented work of art.**. The chosen goal will be revealed globally on Inter Miami CF Foundation’s official social media channels on May 22 at 11:00 AM ET, and will be immortalized through a groundbreaking collaboration with Refik Anadol—a key figure in 21st-century art whose data-sculpted creations have redefined the boundaries of art and technology. The final piece, to be officially unveiled in New York by world's leading auction house Christie’s on June 11, will bear the signature of both artists and will consist of two interconnected elements: the purest visual representation of the goal chosen by Messi, and Anadol’s artistic interpretation generated from the millions of data points linked to that. Led by the Inter Miami CF Foundation, the project A Goal in Life —for which the Foundation invited Leo Messi and Refik Anadol to participate— is under the creative direction of Xavier Roca, with artistic curation by acclaimed art expert Ximena Caminos.","Strong evidence of a brand collaboration involving a well-known athlete and an artist, with a significant fundraising component and a unique creative project.  The use of data-sculpting and Christie’s auction adds significant brand visibility and impact."
