22,ronaldo ,@cristiano,"Instagram, Facebook, Twitter, Premier League, Euro 2020",Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Brand Partnerships,Social Media Engagement,2021-11-01,https://www.newswhip.com/2021/11/how-cristiano-ronaldos-brand-partnerships-influence-customers/,Case Study,75,positive,maybe,73,How Cristiano Ronaldo's brand partnerships influence customers,"We know that Ronaldo earns an immense amount of engagement on his own, but what does it look like when he’s tied to a brand and how does his social media status have an impact? Initially this came as a surprise due to the level of media interest he receives in general, but as we dig a bit deeper it becomes clear that engagement with Ronaldo’s brand partnerships tends to be mostly limited to his own social universe. James only saw 29 million engagements this year, and although that would normally be considered a high level of engagement, it shows how far above and beyond Ronaldo’s level of influence is on social media. In our analysis we’ve seen how content about Ronaldo can quickly erupt, but it seems that media coverage about him leans more towards his life as an athlete and brand partnerships receive engagement through his influence alone.",Strong evidence of brand partnerships and social engagement. Focus on Ronaldo’s influence on his own social universe is noteworthy.
23,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Instagram,Nike,sportswear,brand_launch,video,2023-10-26,https://www.instagram.com/reel/DTDD0ozDZNZ/,paid_partnership,95,positive,yes,78,Cristiano Ronaldo gets his own Nike logo & brand ... - Instagram,"Nike no longer wants Cristiano, and he will create his own brand #nike #ronaldo #soccer #football #player ... [Nike Football] , [Collaboration] ,",Strong evidence of a paid partnership with Nike.  The content explicitly states Nike no longer wants Cristiano and will create his own brand.  #nike #ronaldo #soccer #football #player #brand_launch
24,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Twitter,Egyptian Steel,steel,endorsement,text,2017-01-01,https://www.espn.com/soccer/story/_/id/37466794/cristiano-ronaldo-world-sponsorships-product-endorsements-ronaldo-inc,mixed,75,neutral,maybe,65,The weird and wonderful world of Cristiano Ronaldo's endorsements - ESPN,"# The weird and wonderful world of Cristiano Ronaldo's endorsements. Ronaldo's been endorsing the brand since 2014 (again, terms unknown) and he's quite good at showing off watches in photos that don't really show you much of the actual watch. I can't figure out how popular **""Cristiano Ronaldo: Kick'n'Run""** is but it seems to have a lot of positive reviews for a freemium game that involves booting a ball around what looks like Paris. There's also a Ronaldo-endorsed **phone**, a **cable company** -- seriously, why is he always nearly nude in these?), a partnership with an **online trading** company, some Ronaldo headphones and a brand-new, utterly bizarre screen protector endorsement with something called **Panzer Glass**, which has one tweet (with Ronaldo, of course) and 238 followers. ## Live a Ronaldo-branded lifestyle. And yet it involves Cristiano Ronaldo. that's why I've partnered with the most safety-oriented steel brand #Egyptian\_Steel pic.twitter.com/8MoFjuALNK. -- but Ronaldo is on it.","The text contains various promotional materials supporting Ronaldo's brand partnerships, including endorsements, product mentions, and social media posts.  There are instances of sponsored content, direct product promotion, and engagement with fans."
