27,ronaldo ,@cristiano,website,Nike,sports apparel,advertising,news,2023-10-27,https://m.allfootballapp.com/news/All/Ronaldo%E2%80%99s-endorsements-With-which-companies-does-he-have-sponsorship-deals/2984573,brand tag,75,positive,maybe,73,Ronaldo’s endorsements: With which companies does he have sponsorship deals?| All Football,"# Ronaldo’s endorsements: With which companies does he have sponsorship deals? **Ronaldo has excelled on the field and off of it, with his salary and endorsement deals bringing in staggering sums of money.**. Ronaldo has won seven league titles in three nations and an unbelievable five Champions League trophies in his career. Regarding international appearances and goals scored, Ronaldo is the undisputed leader of his country. ### Who sponsors Cristiano Ronaldo? **Nike is Ronaldo’s main sponsor, allegedly paying him more than $20 million annually. In 2016, Ronaldo became just the third athlete in Nike’s history to sign a lifetime contract**. With Messi representing Nike’s archrival, Adidas, and Neymar now working for Puma, Ronaldo’s affiliation with Nike is crucial. **Currently, Ronaldo receives around $45 million per year in advertising revenues from various sponsors.**. Ronaldo not only makes a lot of money through endorsement deals and his own endeavors but also devotes a lot of time to charitable causes.","Strong evidence of Nike sponsorship through a lifetime contract, substantial annual revenue, and prominent branding across various products.  Also mentions Adobe branding and potential future deals."
