35,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Website,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Brand Partnership/Product Endorsement,Endorsements,April 2026,https://bookingagentinfo.com/celebrity/cristiano-ronaldo/endorsements/,Official Campaign Page,95,positive,yes,78,Cristiano Ronaldo - Complete List of Endorsements,"# Cristiano Ronaldo Endorsements. ## 41 Cristiano Ronaldo Endorsements Deals. Cristiano Ronaldo's endorsement deals have included collaborations with well-known brands such as Advanced Recovery for Athletes - AVA, Armani, and Aroya Cruises. Cristiano Ronaldo has endorsed 41 brands, including prominent names like Advanced Recovery for Athletes - AVA, Armani and Aroya Cruises. ## Brand Categories Endorsed by Cristiano Ronaldo. Read more  Messi, Ronaldo, Mbappé and Vinícius Star in LEGO 2026 World Cup Campaign Celebrity Name: Lionel Messi, Cristiano Ronaldo, Kylian Mbappé, Vinícius Júnior Brand Name: LEGO Deal Type: Global Brand Partnership / Product Endorsement Announced: April 2026 Impact: Expands LEGO’s presence in sports, positions the brand at the heart of World Cup conversation,…. #### What brands has Cristiano Ronaldo endorsed? #### What product types has Cristiano Ronaldo endorsed? Cristiano Ronaldo has endorsed 36 types of products. #### How does Cristiano Ronaldo choose brands to endorse? Celebrities like Cristiano Ronaldo usually select brands that align with their personal values and interests, ensuring a genuine connection with the products and services they endorse or invest in.",Strong evidence of a brand collaboration with multiple brands and a significant endorsement portfolio.
