39,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Social Media,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Brand Partnership/Promotion,Visual,2025-09-01,https://www.harpersbazaar.in/travel-food/story/in-saudis-latest-campaign-cristiano-ronaldo-invites-you-to-stay-for-more-1267264-2025-09-01,Brand Tag/Campaign Page/Event Invitation,75,positive,maybe,73,"In Saudi's latest campaign, Cristiano Ronaldo invites you to “stay for more” - Harpers bazaar","# In Saudi's latest campaign, Cristiano Ronaldo invites you to “stay for more”. ## The Portuguese footballer stars in Saudi's new campaign, unveiling it as a destination that offers everything from sport, culture, and spectacle. Saudi Tourism's latest campaign, starring Cristiano Ronaldo, is a statement in grandeur. A declaration that the country, once defined solely by its passion for football, is now stepping into the global spotlight as a hub for sport, culture, and world-class events. Chic, cinematic, and charged with energy, the campaign captures Ronaldo’s journey of discovery in a land where the future is unfolding in real time. In a country where football ignited the first spark, Saudi Arabia has built a calendar of events that rivals the world’s most dynamic tourist destinations. Today, the truth is, that from the energy of the fans to the scale of ambition — this is where the future of sport is being written.","The text strongly suggests a brand collaboration due to the explicit mention of Ronaldo, the campaign's focus on Saudi Arabia, and the overall tone of the description. However, it’s not a full-blown advertisement; it’s more of a promotional piece."
40,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Web Page,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Brand Promotion,Article,2024-01-26,https://www.arabnews.jp/en/features/article_154408/,"Brand Mention, Campaign Description, Official Statement",75,positive,maybe,73,"‘I came for football, I stayed for more’: Ronaldo headlines Saudi Tourism’s ‘Unreal Calendar’ campaign｜Arab News Japan","* ‘I came for football, I stayed for more’: Ronaldo headlines Saudi Tourism’s ‘Unreal Calendar’ campaign. Ronaldo is featured in Saudi Tourism's new ‘Unreal Calendar’ campaign. RIYADH: Superstar Cristiano Ronaldo is the face of a new Saudi Tourism campaign to showcase the Kingdom’s packed events calendar as the country grows into a major sporting and cultural destination for foreign and domestic travelers. The video wraps up with several non-sporting events for visitors to enjoy, including cultural and heritage activities, as Ronaldo declares: “I came for football, I stayed for more.”. The Saudi Tourism Authority said the campaign will be launched in several key markets in Europe, as well as India and China. “Today, the truth is, that from the energy of the fans to the scale of ambition — this is where the future of sport is being written.”. The Kingdom is investing to become a global hub for sporting and cultural attractions, as a part of the Saudi Vision 2030 plan to diversify the economy and expand the tourism sector.","Strong evidence of a brand collaboration. The text explicitly references Ronaldo, the 'Unreal Calendar' campaign, and the brand’s statement about the Kingdom’s ambitions to become a global sports hub."
41,ronaldo ,@cristiano,News,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Tourism,News Article,2023-10-27,https://indianexpress.com/article/world/saudi-tourism-campaign-featuring-cristiano-ronaldo-10226444/,Brand Promotion,75,positive,maybe,73,Saudi launches new campaign featuring Cristiano Ronaldo to promote year-round tourism | World News - The Indian Express,"# Saudi launches new campaign featuring Cristiano Ronaldo to promote year-round tourism. ## Tourism has been a major focus for the Saudis as part of Crown Prince MBS’s Vision 2030 and committed $800 billion to developing the sector. Saudi launches new campaign featuring Cristiano RonaldoAlong with tourism, Saudi Arabia has also emerged as a major destination for sports and other events. The Saudi Tourism Authority (STA) has launched its latest global campaign starring football legend Cristiano Ronaldo to promote the kingdom as a year-round tourist destination. The campaign, ‘Saudi, Welcome to Arabia’, features Saudi Arabia’s growing calendar of world-class sports, entertainment, culture, and fashion events. ## Saudi’s tourism campaign featuring Cristiano Ronaldo. Tourism has been a major focus for the Saudis as part of Crown Prince MBS’s Vision 2030. Along with tourism, in recent years, Saudi Arabia has also emerged as a major destination for sports and other events.","The text explicitly mentions a 'campaign' featuring Cristiano Ronaldo and its promotion of year-round tourism, suggesting a collaboration with the Saudi Tourism Authority."
