53,ronaldo ,@cristiano,tv,@cristiano,sports,advertising,ad,recent,https://www.adweek.com/creativity/soccer-player-cristiano-ronaldos-latest-ad-captures-the-agony-and-ecstasy-of-sports-fans/,brand mention,75,positive,maybe,73,Cristiano Ronaldo Ad Shows Highs and Lows of Sports Fandom,"# Soccer Player Cristiano Ronaldo’s Latest Ad Captures the Agony and Ecstasy of Sports Fans. ## Campaign for LiveScore shows how making a goal carries more meaning for sports enthusiasts. Cristiano Ronaldo shoots a goal in a soccer game. Soccer champion Cristiano Ronaldo is a frequent star of advertising for brands ranging from Nike to Coca-Cola. He makes his latest commercial appearance in the biggest ever campaign for LiveScore, a global business spanning 200 territories that provides real-time sports updates. This is the brand’s TV ad debut, developed by London-based creative agency Wonderhood Studios and media experience agency Bicycle London after both won the business earlier this year. LiveScore has invested a seven-figure media plan into the campaign, which will air during every live Premier League broadcast this season and on the channels Sky Sports and BT Sport in the U.K. #### Brittaney Kiefer Brittaney is Adweek's creative editor based in London. Brittaney is Adweek's creative editor based in London.",Strong evidence of a brand collaboration. The ad's focus on Cristiano Ronaldo's commercial appearance and LiveScore's media plan suggests a partnership.
