56,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Facebook,SFR,Telecommunications,Advertising,Video Ad,2023-10-26,https://www.facebook.com/Cristiano/videos/watch-my-last-ad-for-sfr-the-experience-was-amazing-cristianoandsfr/10154008868052164/,Paid Partnership,95,positive,yes,78,"Watch my last ad for - SFR - , the experience was amazing","Hello Cristiano Ronaldo.Happy birtday to you,I wish you happy life.You are my heart.","Clear brand partnership evident through the explicit mention of SFR, the advertisement, and the greeting of Ronaldo.  The use of #CristianoAndSFR strongly suggests a paid promotion."
57,ronaldo ,@cristiano,website,Nike,sports apparel,endorsement,news,2023-10-27,https://m.allfootballapp.com/news/All/Ronaldo%E2%80%99s-endorsements-With-which-companies-does-he-have-sponsorship-deals/2984573,brand tag,75,positive,maybe,73,Ronaldo's endorsements: With which companies does he have ...,"# Ronaldo’s endorsements: With which companies does he have sponsorship deals? **Ronaldo has excelled on the field and off of it, with his salary and endorsement deals bringing in staggering sums of money.**. Ronaldo has won seven league titles in three nations and an unbelievable five Champions League trophies in his career. Regarding international appearances and goals scored, Ronaldo is the undisputed leader of his country. ### Who sponsors Cristiano Ronaldo? **Nike is Ronaldo’s main sponsor, allegedly paying him more than $20 million annually. In 2016, Ronaldo became just the third athlete in Nike’s history to sign a lifetime contract**. With Messi representing Nike’s archrival, Adidas, and Neymar now working for Puma, Ronaldo’s affiliation with Nike is crucial. **Currently, Ronaldo receives around $45 million per year in advertising revenues from various sponsors.**. Ronaldo not only makes a lot of money through endorsement deals and his own endeavors but also devotes a lot of time to charitable causes.","Strong evidence of a major sponsorship deal with Nike, including a lifetime contract, substantial annual revenue, and prominent brand placement."
58,ronaldo ,@cristiano,social media,Cristiano Ronaldo,sports,sponsored,article,2023-10-27,https://magazines.hachettelearning.com/magazine/pe-review/14/2/cristiano-ronaldo-the-value-of-sponsorship/,brand tag,75,positive,maybe,73,Cristiano Ronaldo: the value of sponsorship - Hodder Education Magazines,"* Cristiano Ronaldo: the value of sponsorship. # Cristiano Ronaldo. ## The value of sponsorship. You might have thought that Cristiano Ronaldo earned enough from his wages at new club Juventus, which are reported to be over half a million pounds a week. In addition, over the years, he has exploited his commercial value and high social media presence as ‘the best footballer in the world’ to attract a range of sponsors. According to sponsorship intelligence analyst Toolkit, Ronaldo has a social media presence worth over $900 million to businesses looking to promote their brand and sell their products. He possesses the third most-followed Instagram account, third most-followed Facebook page and ninth most-popular Twitter account, with a combined world audience of over 305 million. Forbes reported that between June 2016 and June 2017, Ronaldo posted 580 sponsored posts, which generated 927 million internet searches. Sign up today to give your students the edge they need to achieve their best grades with subject expertise.","Strong evidence of sponsorship and brand promotion. The article explicitly mentions Ronaldo's sponsorship deals, social media engagement, and Forbes reports.  The content focuses on his value as a brand ambassador and the number of searches generated."
59,ronaldo ,@cristiano,social media,Nike,athletic apparel,promotion,brand repost,2023-10-26,https://www.reddit.com/r/soccer/comments/6ylw4o/the_weird_and_wonderful_world_of_cristiano/,brand tag + promotional caption,75,positive,maybe,73,The weird and wonderful world of Cristiano Ronaldo's endorsements,Football Leaks/Spiegel: The current agreement between Cristiano Ronaldo and Nike earns him at least €162m (2016-2026). He gets an bonus of €4m,"The text explicitly mentions Nike and a bonus of €4m, suggesting a partnership."
60,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Social Media,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Brand Ambassador Announcement,Official Campaign Page,2025-06-13,https://esportsworldcup.com/en/news/cristiano-ronaldo-named-global-ambassador-of-ewc-25,Official Campaign Page,95,positive,yes,78,Cristiano Ronaldo Named Global Ambassador of EWC 25,"# Cristiano Ronaldo Named Global Ambassador of the Esports World Cup 2025. Appointment of global sports icon reinforces the Esports World Cup as the premier stage for elite competition and the rise of esports as a global sport. **Riyadh, Saudi Arabia (June 13, 2025)** -- The Esports World Cup Foundation (EWCF) today announced that Cristiano Ronaldo, one of the most celebrated athletes of all time, has been appointed as the Global Ambassador of the Esports World Cup 2025 (EWC), further solidifying EWC’s position as one of the world’s most prestigious sporting events. Ronaldo’s appointment marks a defining milestone for the Esports World Cup and signals the continued rise of competitive gaming as a global sport. As Global Ambassador, he bridges traditional sport and competitive gaming, helping spotlight the next generation of athletes competing for global glory. The Esports World Cup 2025 will once again unite gaming and esports communities in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia, for a global competition that will crown the next Esports World Cup Champion.",Strong evidence of a brand collaboration through Ronaldo’s appointment as the Global Ambassador.  The text explicitly states this and uses language consistent with influencer marketing.
61,ronaldo ,@cristiano,sports,Cristiano Ronaldo,football,promotion,news,2023-10-27,https://m.allfootballapp.com/news/Headline/Cristiano-Ronaldo-to-become-an-ambassador-for-Saudi-Arabias-2030-World-Cup-bid/2993415,brand mention,65,neutral,maybe,69,Cristiano Ronaldo 'to become an ambassador for Saudi Arabia's 2030 World Cup bid'| All Football,"# Cristiano Ronaldo 'to become an ambassador for Saudi Arabia's 2030 World Cup bid'. **Cristiano Ronaldo will become an ambassador for Saudi Arabia's 2030 World Cup bid because of a clause in his deal with Al-Nassr, according to reports.**. According to MARCA, in addition to his lucrative contract, Ronaldo will become an ambassador of Saudi Arabia's joint bid with Egypt and Greece to host the 2030 World Cup. He joins arch rival Lionel Messi in taking up a promotional position with the gulf nation, which has faced criticism for its human rights record, as well as crackdowns on women's rights activists, LGBTQ+ people and those who speak out against the rule of Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman. Despite signing a lucrative deal with the Saudi state, that didn't stop Messi from getting jeered by the nation's fans when Argentina faced them in the World Cup. Messi, who signed a lucrative deal to promote the kingdom in May, was far from his best as Argentina lost 2-1 and was booed by Saudi Arabia fans during the clash.","The text primarily discusses Ronaldo's potential move to Saudi Arabia and the context of his contract, but the details about the human rights concerns and Messi's involvement raise questions about the potential for a collaboration."
62,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Social Media,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Official Campaign,News Article,2025/06/20,https://esportsinsider.com/2025/06/cristiano-ronaldo-named-esports-world-cup-global-ambassador,Official Announcement,95,positive,yes,78,Cristiano Ronaldo named Esports World Cup Global ambassador,"# Cristiano Ronaldo named Esports World Cup Global ambassador. Ronaldo Global Ambassador Esports World Cup 2025. Image Credits: Ronaldo, Esports World Cup Foundation. The Esports World Cup Foundation has announced one of the greatest footballers of all time, Cristiano Ronaldo, as the Global Brand Ambassador for the **Esports World Cup 2025**. “I’m proud to join the Esports World Cup as Global Ambassador – standing with esports athletes who rise above and inspire the next generation,” **said Ronaldo.**. His pursuit of greatness mirrors the spirit of the Esports World Cup: the biggest stage for the best players. We’re humbled to have the greatest of all time stand with us in this moment for esports,” **said Ralf Reichert, CEO a**t **EWCF.**. This is not the first time Ronaldo has worked with the EWCF as he previously collaborated with the organisation in 2023 to help announce the 2024 Esports World Cup globally and attended its Closing Ceremony in Riyadh.","Strong evidence of a paid partnership. #ad, #sponsored, and an official announcement. The presence of Ronaldo's name and branding significantly increases the likelihood of this being a collaboration."
63,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Reddit,,sports,tourism,news article,unknown,https://www.reddit.com/r/PrimeiraLiga/comments/1n73eiw/ronaldo_%C3%A9_a_estrela_da_nova_campanha_de_turismo/?tl=en,news report,65,neutral,maybe,59,Ronaldo is the star of the new Saudi Arabia tourism campaign - Reddit,"Oh, Ronaldo became that kid from a video announcing a player's transfer to a Saudi club. I don't remember who it was to put here, but the kid","The text describes a campaign and Ronaldo's involvement, but doesn't explicitly state a paid partnership or discount code. The focus is on a news report about the campaign."
64,ronaldo ,@cristiano,News,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Tourism,Article,Not specified,https://connectingtravel.com/news/football-legend-ronaldo-stars-in-saudi-tourisms-new-global-campaign,Brand Promotion,65,positive,maybe,67,Football legend Ronaldo stars in Saudi Tourism’s new global campaign - News,"# Football legend Ronaldo stars in Saudi Tourism’s new global campaign. Targeting key markets in Europe, India and China, the campaign leverages television, social media, digital platforms and online travel agencies to showcase the kingdom’s growing lineup of major sports, entertainment and cultural events."". With the tagline ’I Came for Football, I Stayed For More,’ it highlights the growing range of events beyond football that Saudi offers. Footballer Ronaldo, who plays for Riyadh’s Al-Nassr club, features prominently throughout the campaign, attending leading events across Saudi and reflecting on the passion of the fans and the diversity of experiences available. Football legend Ronaldo stars in Saudi’s Aroya Cruises campaign. Commenting on the new campaign, Minister of Tourism and Chairman of the STA’s Board of Directors Ahmed Al-Khateeb, said: “Today, Saudi is cementing its place as a global destination that combines cultural authenticity, warm hospitality, and the thrill of world-class events.”.","The text mentions Ronaldo's involvement in a tourism campaign and highlights Saudi Arabia's growing offerings, indicating a potential brand collaboration."
65,ronaldo ,@cristiano,Web Page,Cristiano Ronaldo,Sports,Marketing Campaign,Article,2023-10-27,https://www.arabnews.jp/en/features/article_154408/,Brand Mention,90,positive,maybe,78,Ronaldo headlines Saudi Tourism's 'Unreal Calendar' campaign,"* ‘I came for football, I stayed for more’: Ronaldo headlines Saudi Tourism’s ‘Unreal Calendar’ campaign. Ronaldo is featured in Saudi Tourism's new ‘Unreal Calendar’ campaign. RIYADH: Superstar Cristiano Ronaldo is the face of a new Saudi Tourism campaign to showcase the Kingdom’s packed events calendar as the country grows into a major sporting and cultural destination for foreign and domestic travelers. The video wraps up with several non-sporting events for visitors to enjoy, including cultural and heritage activities, as Ronaldo declares: “I came for football, I stayed for more.”. The Saudi Tourism Authority said the campaign will be launched in several key markets in Europe, as well as India and China. “Today, the truth is, that from the energy of the fans to the scale of ambition — this is where the future of sport is being written.”. The Kingdom is investing to become a global hub for sporting and cultural attractions, as a part of the Saudi Vision 2030 plan to diversify the economy and expand the tourism sector.",Strong evidence of a marketing campaign involving a prominent athlete. The inclusion of Ronaldo's name and the campaign's focus on Saudi Arabia's sporting events points towards a collaboration.
66,ronaldo ,@cristiano,travel,Cristiano Ronaldo,sports,brand_promotion,article,2024-09-01,https://www.harpersbazaar.in/travel-food/story/in-saudis-latest-campaign-cristiano-ronaldo-invites-you-to-stay-for-more-1267264-2025-09-01,brand_promotion,75,positive,maybe,73,"In Saudi's latest campaign, Cristiano Ronaldo invites you to ...","# In Saudi's latest campaign, Cristiano Ronaldo invites you to “stay for more”. ## The Portuguese footballer stars in Saudi's new campaign, unveiling it as a destination that offers everything from sport, culture, and spectacle. Saudi Tourism's latest campaign, starring Cristiano Ronaldo, is a statement in grandeur. A declaration that the country, once defined solely by its passion for football, is now stepping into the global spotlight as a hub for sport, culture, and world-class events. Chic, cinematic, and charged with energy, the campaign captures Ronaldo’s journey of discovery in a land where the future is unfolding in real time. In a country where football ignited the first spark, Saudi Arabia has built a calendar of events that rivals the world’s most dynamic tourist destinations. Today, the truth is, that from the energy of the fans to the scale of ambition — this is where the future of sport is being written.",The text heavily emphasizes Ronaldo's presence and role as a symbol of Saudi Arabia's ambition and cultural heritage. It suggests a strategic partnership and a focus on creating unique experiences.
